Tiffany Ariana Trump, daughter of the former President of the United States of America, Donald Trump, has announced her engagement to her Fiancé, Micheal Boulos. Tiffany who is also Trump’s only child with his second wife, Marla Maples, made the announcement in a post via her Instagram account on Wednesday. She also thanked the people of America for celebrating many milestones, historic occasions and creating memories with her family during their stay at the White House. “It has been such an honor to celebrate many milestones, historic occasions and creating memories with my family during our stay at the White House. “It’s also an honor to announce my engagement to my amazing fiancé Micheal. “I am feeling blessed, and I look forward to the next chapter of our lives,” she said. 